author: 滇西小哥 Dianxi Xiaoge
description:
※Click "cc" on the lower right menu to choose your subtitle language.

Among all the wild mushrooms of Yunnan, which is the most precious? Ganba Mushroom is one of them. On the market, its price can reach up to 2000 yuan per kilogram. With its unique appearance and rich aroma, just one bite of Ganba Mushroom captures the very essence of Yunnan’s mountains and forests. Each mushroom in Yunnan carries its own special role, and the best way to cook Ganba Mushroom is to make fried rice… That bowl of rice, bursting with fragrance, fills the tongue with joy and can make you happy for an entire year.

Hello, everyone! I am Dianxi Xiaoge, a Yunnan native. If you enjoy my videos, please keep subscribing to my channel. I'll continue to share my life and Yunnan-styled food in my uploads. Wish you have a happy life and enjoy tasty food every day
